Package org.apache.qpid.protonj2.codec.encoders

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PrimitiveTypeEncoder<V>
    Marker interface for an encoder of Primitive types such as Integer or Boolean
    UTF8Encoder
    Interface for an external UTF8 Encoder that can be supplied by a client which implements custom encoding logic optimized for the application using the Codec.

    AbstractDescribedTypeEncoder<V>

    AbstractPrimitiveTypeEncoder<V>

    DeliveryTagEncoder
    Custom encoder for writing DeliveryTag types to a ProtonBuffer.
    ProtonEncoder
    The default AMQP Encoder implementation.
    ProtonEncoderFactory
    Factory that create and initializes new BuiltinEncoder instances
    ProtonEncoderState
    State object used by the Built in Encoder implementation.
    UnknownDescribedTypeEncoder
    Encoder of AMQP Described Types to a byte stream.
